  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* poly20: an arbitrary degree-20 test polynomial in u with random rational coefficients,\n   used only as a stand-in workload to validate/benchmark the residue-evaluation\n   approaches below (n plays the role of a generic monomial degree, not a physical\n   quantum number) *)\nSeedRandom[42];\npoly20 = Sum[RandomInteger[{-20, 20}]/RandomInteger[{1, 10}] u^k, {k, 0, 20}]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
