  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "## Integrating poly20 against e^{wu}/((u-1)^S1 u^S2)\n\nThree approaches, benchmarked at S1=S2=8: (1) direct `Residue` on the whole rational·exponential expression, (2) term-by-term via the closed-form `res1`/`res0` (Laguerre) formulas, (3) a proposed truncated-power-series / convolution approach that avoids both generic `Residue` and symbolic `LaguerreL`/Gamma overhead.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "polyCoeffs = CoefficientList[poly20, u]; (* index i = coefficient of u^i, i=0..20 *)\nLength[polyCoeffs]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"50770\" data-output-id=\"37\" data-out-n=\"48\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"7\" data-sub-start=\"1\" data-sub-end=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[48]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrggrlkw-e6td8se\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"MjE=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">21</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[48]= 21",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "08221340-1e31-47cc-a71e-59dad38083ac"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* Approach 1: direct Residue on the full expression *)\nAbsoluteTiming[\n  direct88 = Residue[poly20 Exp[w u]/((u - 1)^8 u^8), {u, 1}] +\n             Residue[poly20 Exp[w u]/((u - 1)^8 u^8), {u, 0}] // Simplify;\n]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"50770\" data-output-id=\"38\" data-out-n=\"49\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"8\" data-sub-start=\"1\" data-sub-end=\"4\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[49]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrggrlya-8fmcl1j\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezAuMDMwODUxLFxtYXRocm17TnVsbH1ccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0.030851</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Null</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[49]= \\left\\{0.030851,\\mathrm{Null}\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
