  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "### Push to large k (guard each method with TimeConstrained so one slow method doesn't block the others)",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "scalingBig = Table[\n   {k,\n    TimeConstrained[AbsoluteTiming[Residue[poly20 Exp[w u]/((u - 1)^k u^k), {u, 1}] +\n         Residue[poly20 Exp[w u]/((u - 1)^k u^k), {u, 0}];][[1]], 30, \"timeout\"],\n    TimeConstrained[AbsoluteTiming[Sum[polyCoeffs[[n + 1]] (res1[n, k, k] + res0[n, k, k]), {n, 0, 20}];][[1]], 30, \"timeout\"],\n    TimeConstrained[AbsoluteTiming[fastResidue[poly20, k, k, w];][[1]], 30, \"timeout\"]\n    },\n   {k, {50, 100, 200, 400}}\n   ];\nGrid[Prepend[scalingBig, {\"S1=S2\", \"direct Residue (s)\", \"closed-form Laguerre (s)\", \"fastResidue (s)\"}], Frame -> All]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
