  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "### Bonus: does specializing w to a number help further (k=400)?",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "wnum = 1.7;\nAbsoluteTiming[direct400num = (Residue[poly20 Exp[w u]/((u - 1)^400 u^400), {u, 1}] +\n     Residue[poly20 Exp[w u]/((u - 1)^400 u^400), {u, 0}]) /. w -> wnum;]\nAbsoluteTiming[closed400num = Sum[polyCoeffs[[n + 1]] (res1[n, 400, 400] + res0[n, 400, 400]), {n, 0, 20}] /. w -> wnum;]\nAbsoluteTiming[closed400numDirect = Sum[polyCoeffs[[n + 1]] (Exp[wnum] LaguerreL[400 - 1, n - 800 + 1, -wnum] +\n       If[400 > n, (-1)^(400 + 400 - n + 1) LaguerreL[400 - n - 1, 1 - 800 + n, wnum], 0]), {n, 0, 20}];]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
